# CRMS – RESUME PARSING & INTELLIGENCE SYSTEM
### Final Architecture Document v2.0 (Revised & Improved)

---

## 📌 SYSTEM OBJECTIVE

| # | Objective |
|---|---|
| 1 | Parse resume PDF into structured machine-readable format |
| 2 | Standardize skill representation via hierarchical taxonomy |
| 3 | Generate semantic embeddings (section-level + global) |
| 4 | Evaluate candidate profile against job description |
| 5 | Score candidate using calibrated evidence-based logic |
| 6 | Rank applicants per job |
| 7 | Suggest shortlist with explainable reasoning |
| 8 | Allow HR override at every decision point |
| 9 | Support future ML-based calibration via feedback loop |
| 10 | Provide full audit trail & explainability dashboard |

---

