# 🖥️ TECHNOLOGY STACK SUMMARY

| Component | Technology | Purpose |
|---|---|---|
| **Backend API** | FastAPI (Python) | REST API for all operations |
| **Job Queue** | Celery + Redis | Async resume processing |
| **Database** | PostgreSQL | Structured data storage |
| **Cache** | Redis | Embedding cache, JD cache, session management |
| **PDF Extraction** | PyMuPDF + pdfplumber | Text extraction from PDFs |
| **OCR** | EasyOCR + Tesseract | Scanned document handling |
| **NLP** | spaCy | Text cleaning, tokenization |
| **NER Model** | Fine-tuned DistilBERT | Resume entity extraction |
| **Embedding Model** | Sentence-BERT (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | Semantic similarity |
| **Frontend** | React.js + Vite | HR Dashboard |
| **Monitoring** | Prometheus + Grafana | System health, model latency |
| **File Storage** | AWS S3 / GCP Cloud Storage | Resume PDF storage |
| **Deployment** | Docker + Docker Compose | Containerized deployment |
| **CI/CD** | GitHub Actions | Automated testing & deployment |

