# 💰 COST BREAKDOWN (Revised)

## Monthly Infrastructure Cost

| Component | Service | Monthly Cost (INR) |
|---|---|---|
| Compute Server | AWS EC2 t3.large (2 vCPU, 8GB RAM) | ₹6,000 |
| Database | PostgreSQL (RDS Small / Self-hosted) | ₹2,000 |
| Cache | Redis (ElastiCache Small / Self-hosted) | ₹1,200 |
| File Storage | S3 (≤10 GB/month growth) | ₹500 |
| Monitoring | CloudWatch / Self-hosted Prometheus | ₹500 |
| Backup & DR | Automated DB + S3 backups | ₹500 |
| SSL / Domain | Certificate + DNS | ₹200 |
| **Total (without LLM)** | | **₹10,900/month** |
| Optional: LLM (GPT for summaries) | OpenAI API (~3,000 resumes/month) | ₹1,200 |
| **Total (with LLM)** | | **₹12,100/month** |

## Cost Per Resume

| Scenario | Monthly Cost | Resumes/Month | Cost/Resume |
|---|---|---|---|
| Without LLM | ₹10,900 | 3,000 | **₹3.63** |
| With LLM | ₹12,100 | 3,000 | **₹4.03** |
| High volume (no LLM) | ₹10,900 | 6,000 | **₹1.82** |

## Model Compute Cost

| Model | License | API Cost | Per-Resume Cost |
|---|---|---|---|
| DistilBERT (fine-tuned) | Open-source (Apache 2.0) | ₹0 | ₹0 |
| Sentence-BERT (all-MiniLM-L6-v2) | Open-source (Apache 2.0) | ₹0 | ₹0 |
| **Total model cost** | | | **₹0** (included in server cost) |

## One-Time Development Cost

| Phase | Effort | Description |
|---|---|---|
| Phase 1: Core Pipeline | 2–3 weeks | Layers 1–4 implementation |
| Phase 2: Scoring + Dashboard | 2–3 weeks | Layer 5 + Explainability UI |
| Phase 3: Feedback Loop | 1–2 weeks | Layer 6 + A/B testing |
| Phase 4: NER Fine-tuning | 2–3 weeks | Data labeling + model training |
| **Total** | **7–11 weeks** | |

## Cost Scaling Triggers

| Trigger | Impact | Solution |
|---|---|---|
| Resume volume > 500/day | CPU bottleneck | Upgrade to t3.xlarge (+₹3,000/month) |
| Resume volume > 1,000/day | Needs multiple workers | Auto-scaling group (+₹5,000/month) |
| GPU models (future) | Significant cost increase | GPU instance (+₹15,000–₹30,000/month) |
| GPT for scoring (not recommended) | API cost explosion | Avoid — use deterministic scoring |
| Real-time vector search | Need dedicated vector DB | Qdrant/Milvus (+₹3,000/month) |

